OL,3,CAmy Schumer diagnosis: What is
OL,4,CCushing's syndrome?
OL,6,FSchumer said she felt "reborn" after
OL,7,Fher diagnosis. But what is Cushing's
OL,8,Fsyndrome and what are the symptoms of
OL,9,Fthe condition? ITV News explains.
OL,11,FWhat is Cushing's syndrome?
OL,13,FCushing's syndrome is a condition
OL,14,Fcaused by having too much of a hormone
OL,15,Fcalled cortisol in your body. It can
OL,16,Fbe serious if it's not treated, .
OL,18,FThe condition is uncommon. It mostly
OL,19,Faffects people who have been taking
OL,20,Fsteroid medicine, especially steroid
OL,21,Ftablets, for a long time.
