OL,3,CAmy Schumer diagnosis: What is
OL,4,CCushing's syndrome?
OL,6,FIt is advised that you do not stop
OL,7,Ftaking your medicine without getting
OL,8,Fmedical advice.
OL,10,FLots of things can cause similar
OL,11,Fsymptoms to Cushing's syndrome, so the
OL,12,FNHS recommends getting checked to find
OL,13,Fout what the problem is before acting
OL,14,Fon it.
OL,16,FIs Cushing's syndrome treatable?
OL,18,FAccording to the NHS, Cushing's
OL,19,Fsyndrome usually gets better with
OL,20,Ftreatment, although treatment depends
OL,21,Fon what's causing it.
